@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_spivej(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.abs(wp.abs(tmp + 0.84)))
    tmp = v1
    v2 = 0.15
    v0 = ((v0 - (tmp + 0.17 / v2 + 0.13)) / wp.abs((tmp + 0.11 + v2 + 0.53)))
    v1 = 0.29
    v2 = 0.17
    data[tid] = v0
